result.name: Tasty Congee & Noodle Wantun Shop

reviews.text: Quality of ingredients was amazing. However, the Mushroom and Chicken Congee (北菇雞粥) I had was disappointing. There were only 4 pieces of chicken and 2 mushrooms, which is unacceptable by Hong Kong's standards. Highly recommend the Singaporean Stir Fried Vermicelli in Curry Powder (星洲炒米) and the Stir Fried Flat Rice Noodles with Beef (乾炒牛河). It was full of 'wok power' (鑊氣), which means good flavour and cooked at a high temperature.
just the taste of chinese food is amoung the best in hongkong , freshly made , nice flavour , small but clean , good service , pleasant staff great idea to go and try and see for yourself difference
Good congee and well known for their rice rolls and charsiu puffs
Good taste good service A bit expensive
One of the best wonton noodles restaurant in HK, but quite expensive

result.name: 正斗粥麵專家

reviews.text: 試了一個細雲吞面，其實吃不到任何鹼水味，做得很好吃，別看小小一顆雲吞，每顆裡面都有2隻蝦，非常足料。而且叫一個小的雲吞面就有4顆 d(ŐдŐ๑) 讚！ 如果真的受不了任何鹼水面味的話可以選牛腩雲吞面，牛腩湯底濃，又可以試到蛋面的味道。

Quality of ingredients was amazing. However, the Mushroom and Chicken Congee (北菇雞粥) I had was disappointing. There were only 4 pieces of chicken and 2 mushrooms, which is unacceptable by Hong Kong's standards. Highly recommend the Singaporean Stir Fried Vermicelli in Curry Powder (星洲炒米) and the Stir Fried Flat Rice Noodles with Beef (乾炒牛河). It was full of 'wok power' (鑊氣), which means good flavour and cooked at a high temperature.
地點適當食材OK粥品、炒作各種多變化各位不妨一試
just the taste of chinese food is amoung the best in hongkong , freshly made , nice flavour , small but clean , good service , pleasant staff great idea to go and try and see for yourself difference
跑馬地“正斗”。。除了“全蛋麵”麵質，淥麵手工有相當高水準之外，雲吞外型精緻飽滿。只可惜雲吞蝦仁有啲霉囗，豬肉餡比例太少，影響雲吞味道。另外麵湯內麻油味太重，落豬油撈麵撈得不均勻。令到湯太油膩。。。
